&lt;p&gt;The 3.0 patch unit tests slightly differ from the other branches as the 3.0 require the static columns to always be read even if they are not queried.&lt;br/&gt;
The 4.0 patch logic handle range deletion in a different way than the other branches due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-15369&quot; title=&quot;Fake row deletions and range tombstones, causing digest mismatch and sstable growth&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-15369&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-15369&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; that modified the logic in the 4.0 branch. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
